        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does CloudTalk cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk offers tiered pricing plans starting from a competitive rate per user per month, billed annually. They have a Starter plan for basic needs, an Essential plan with more advanced features like power dialing, and a custom Expert plan. You can see all details and start a free trial on their website.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use CloudTalk on my mobile phone?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, CloudTalk has dedicated mobile apps for iOS and Android. This allows your agents to make and receive business calls, access contact info, and use key features from anywhere, which is perfect for remote or field-based teams.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is call recording with CloudTalk legal?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk provides the tools for call recording, but compliance with local laws is your responsibility. The platform allows you to configure recording settings (e.g., automatic with a beep notification, manual, or disabled) to help you adhere to regulations like GDPR. Always inform callers of the recording according to your jurisdiction's laws.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
